channel.title: RS2HD 525 - Walking, Force chat, Equipment!
channel.description:
Features :- Rendering NPC updating. Multiplayer updating. Walking. Public chat. Items on interface. Skill level display. SendMessage packet. Graphic update mask. Animation update mask. Force text update mask. Hit update mask 1. Hit update mask 2. FaceTo update mask. They are player masks, not NPC masks! Actionbutton packet. NPC click packets. Item equipping. Ground items. All Object clicking packets. Most item packets. Commands - gfx #, pickup # #, emote #, tele # #, inter #
Add NPC attacking yourselves. Because it crashes when you attack an npc. I recommend using RS2HD framework, Not palidino76's v1 525; As there is only class files.
You [b]need[/b] the client download here : http://uppit.com/4YG0RL (100 % Credits to [b]Luke132[/b] from Rune server) If you don't have the cache, It can be found here : http://www.megaupload.com/?d=TGJ2PGCB
RS2HD Framework, The recommended server; Can be downloaded here http://uppit.com/YI19JT (100 % Credits to [b]Luke132[/b] from Rune server)
Palidino76's 525 V1 can be found here : http://uppit.com/7P56Y3 (100% to Palidino76)
[IMG]http://img19.imageshack.us/img19/2254/screenshot054qn3.png[/img] [IMG]http://i183.photobucket.com/albums/x34/luke_livez/loltake.jpg[/img]
[size=14pt][b]100% Credits to Luke132 from Rune Server. I am just posting it here![/size]
Enjoy!
P.S. This server is VERY basic. Most of the equipment [b]Doesn't[/b] work. I have the ID's for itemDefinitions; If you want those, Please feel free to send me a PM.
